{"tid":1230420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"百人到美國駐港總領事館門外請願　斥美方煽動港人犯法","createTime":"2019-06-16T07:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:01:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":595,"uniUserReply":137,"replies":[{"pid":"bbda4cd663c624d88a84410147ac874b2b1e6185","tid":1230420,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190616/photo/bkn-20190616103858099-0616_00822_001_01b.jpg?20190616111854\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190616%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190616103858099-0616_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20190616111854&h=20097b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國近日多次就港府修訂《逃犯條例》表達關注及憂慮。有團體及政黨一行約100人趁今天(16日)父親節，到美國駐港總領事館門外請願，批評美國政府干預香港內部事務，促請美國政府「收手」，不要煽動年輕人捲入政治漩渦。請願人士在領事館外貼上心意卡後散去。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會會長兼活動發起人吳秋北直斥美國煽動香港年輕人示威，「612暴動」中多人掟磚及鐵欄，做出非法暴力行為，涉嫌觸犯法律或影響前途，令父母痛心。他批評美國行為可恥，更令部分家庭分裂。<br />\n<br />\n家庭團聚互助會亦強烈譴責美國干涉香港內部事務，批評美國政府妖言惑眾抹黑修例，煽動港人犯法。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190616/bkn-20190616103858099-0616_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190616%2Fbkn-20190616103858099-0616_00822_001.html&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=fab790b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190616/bkn-20190616103858099-0616_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"29cd92b17cdd30c01e359c533749152212ec176b","tid":1230420,"uid":229955,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9hCJKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9hCJKF.jpg&h=0756c303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231862ffd7d0fe5275b3e5dd2823b07a0d5e8819","tid":1230420,"uid":76216,"like":429,"dislike":1,"score":428,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"哩100個就收錢啦<br />\n<br />\n100萬人有錢收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a4f713a34e197a2bbf3b8e051b74ef20b2ba87","tid":1230420,"uid":2419,"like":339,"dislike":0,"score":339,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"佢地唔係扮架喎 真係戇鳩架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3320b78c3889225bda44b2fc472aa4c72cfad26a","tid":1230420,"uid":6548,"like":267,"dislike":0,"score":267,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:40:22.000Z","msg":"美國心諗 成班傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927987e41fafe63bdef02382a8aa839d62aa622e","tid":1230420,"uid":259900,"like":125,"dislike":0,"score":125,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"工聯會話人暴動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101fa6d4fec9d36d1f4946b6ab9bfcadaf953be3","tid":1230420,"uid":37592,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"美國:堅決反對別國干預我國內政!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1299f6ca9d37e78557ccc8d9df1ecd6bd2e38a","tid":1230420,"uid":184787,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T07:41:21.000Z","msg":"咁多人支持修例<br />\n建議號召支持個80萬人，前往民陣遊行隊伍前方保護政府"},{"pid":"b78a6dc700d41b52be074e5d3